# [[then]] {{gloss|connecting two verbs or verb-phrases}}; [[and]]
#* {{zh-x|賜 不幸 言 而 中{zhòng}。|As ill fortune had it, {{w|Duanmu Ci|Ci}} spoke of this, '''then''' his words turned out to be true.|ref=Zuozhuan}}
# [[and]] [[yet]]; [[but]]; [[nevertheless]] {{gloss|conjunction indicating [[concession]] or [[contrast]]}}
#: {{zh-x|有 其 名 而 無 其實|in name '''but''' not in reality}}
#* {{zh-x|心 猶豫 而 狐疑 兮，欲 自適 而 不可。|Like whelp in doubt''',''' like timid fox in fear,<br>I wished to go, '''but''' wandered ever near.|ref=Chuci}}
#* {{zh-x|君子 易 知 而 難 狎，易 懼 而 難 脅，畏 患 而 不-避 義-死，欲 利 而 不-為{wéi} 所-非，交 親 而 不 比，言 辯 而 不 辭。|Those who are superior in character can be easily understood '''but''' cannot be approached with inappropriate familiarity; they are often timid and cautious, '''but''' cannot be threatened; they fear peril '''but''' are ready to die for a righteous cause; they desire what is beneficial, '''but''' choose not to achieve it by means they disapprove of; they befriend acquaintances '''but''' do not form cliques; they speak with eloquence '''but''' without flourish.|ref=Xunzi}}
# [[to]] {{gloss|often used with {{zh-m|*自}}}}
#: {{zh-x|自上而下|from top '''to''' bottom; [[top-down]]}}
# {{n-g|particle between adverbial element and verb to indicate cause, purpose, or manner}}
#: {{zh-x|半途而廢|to give up halfway}}
#: {{zh-x|不幸而言中{zhòng}|to make an accurate prediction despite its unfortunate nature}}
#* {{zh-x|吾 嘗 終日 而 思 矣，不如 須臾 之 所-學 也。|I used to contemplate all day long only to obtain no more than what can be achieved with learning in a short while.|ref=Xunzi}}
#* {{zh-x|昔 ^孔子 何為{wèi} 而 作 《^春秋》 哉？|At that time, for what purpose did Confucius compile the ''{{w|Spring and Autumn Annals|Spring and Autumn}}''?|ref=Shiji}}
## {{n-g|particle between two verbs or verb phrases indicating that the first is used adverbially}}
##: {{zh-x|不得其門而入|to fail to understand|lit=to be unable to enter by finding the gate}}
