# {{n-g|modal particle indicating [[tendency]] or [[immediate]] action}}
#* {{zh-x|此 三 子 者，皆 布衣 之 士 也；懷 怒 未 發，休 祲 降{jiàng} 於 天，與 臣 而 將{jiāng} 四 矣。|All of those three worthy men were heroes among humble commoners who, having not even released their wrath, saw omens auspicious to their heroic deeds and ruinous to their opponents dispatched by Heaven. Now, with me, there '''is about to''' be a fourth.|ref=Zhanguoce}}

